---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service & Disclaimer | Net Worth Calculator by Age" description="Terms of service and financial benchmark disclaimer for NetWorth.">
	<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-20">
		<header class="text-center mb-12 space-y-2">
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">Terms of Service & Financial Disclaimer</h1>
			<p class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-400">Effective Date: {new Date().getFullYear()}</p>
		</header>

		<div class="p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800/80 bg-white/95 dark:bg-slate-900/60 shadow-xl backdrop-blur-xl text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-300 space-y-6 font-normal leading-relaxed">
			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">1. Educational & Benchmark Purpose Only</h2>
				<p>NetWorth is provided for informational and benchmark comparison purposes only. Calculations are based on statistical sampling from the US Federal Reserve Survey of Consumer Finances (SCF). This tool does not constitute individualized financial, investment, tax, or legal advice.</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">2. No Financial Advisor Relationship</h2>
				<p>Use of this site does not create a fiduciary or financial advisor relationship. Always consult a certified financial planner (CFP) or tax professional for your personal financial planning.</p>
			</section>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
